<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="138" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="23.[140,1108,236,440]" pageId="23" pageNumber="138">
<bibRefCitation author="Smetana" box="[185,369,272,299]" firstAuthor="Smetana" pageId="23" pageNumber="138" pagination="1 - 946" refId="ref18100" refString="Smetana A (1995) Rove beetles of the subtribe Philonthina of America north of Mexico (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) classification, phylogeny and taxonomic revision. Memoirs on Entomology International 3: i-x, 1 - 946." type="journal article" year="1995">Smetana (1995)</bibRefCitation>
observed that this species is found in a wide range of habitats. 
<bibRefCitation author="Davies" box="[140,304,307,333]" firstAuthor="Davies" pageId="23" pageNumber="138" refId="ref16041" refString="Davies, A (1979. A study of the staphylinid beetles occurring in decaying seaweed on the shore of Passamaquoddy Bay (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). BSc thesis, Ottawa, Ontario: Carleton University." type="book" year="1979">Davies (1979)</bibRefCitation>
found this species was frequent in coastal beach-wrack habitats, but also found in other environments, in St. Andrews, New Brunswick. It has not been noted as a coastal species in 
<collectingCountry box="[453,601,378,404]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="23" pageNumber="138">Great Britain</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hammond" box="[616,813,378,404]" firstAuthor="Hammond" pageId="23" pageNumber="138" pagination="247 - 302" refId="ref16451" refString="Hammond PM (2000) Coastal Staphylinidae (rove beetles) in the British Isles, with special reference to saltmarshes. In: Sherwood BR, Gardiner BG, Harris T (Eds) British Saltmarshes: Joint symposium on British Saltmarshes organized between the Linnean Society of London, the Royal Society for the Protection of Birds, and English Nature. Cardigan, London, 247 - 302." type="book chapter" year="2000">Hammond 2000</bibRefCitation>
). Its distribution in North America is shown in 
<bibRefCitation author="Smetana" box="[376,561,413,440]" firstAuthor="Smetana" pageId="23" pageNumber="138" pagination="1 - 946" refId="ref18100" refString="Smetana A (1995) Rove beetles of the subtribe Philonthina of America north of Mexico (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae) classification, phylogeny and taxonomic revision. Memoirs on Entomology International 3: i-x, 1 - 946." type="journal article" year="1995">Smetana (1995)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
